# Screening workstream

You are building the **screening app** — questionnaire, scoring, results, booking, PDF.

## Before building

1. Run **bridge-hub-onboard** skill (unless full context already).
2. Use [docs/roadmap_screening.md](docs/roadmap_screening.md) for build phase checklist.
3. Use [specs/cursor-guide/FILE_OVERVIEW.md](specs/cursor-guide/FILE_OVERVIEW.md) for authoritative specs.
4. Locked decisions in `specs/cursor-guide/` are final.

- Scoring, AI (OpenRouter), and PDF generation **server-side only**
- PDF on booking confirmation only — never before
- Assessment forward-only — auto-save every answer
- Supabase EU. Service role never in client components

## Must not

- Edit `app/(marketing)/` or `components/marketing/` unless explicitly coordinating
- Import marketing Framer Motion components into screening flows

## Copy

- Disclaimer on every screen
- Client Layer 2: `specs/chat-05/chat-05-layer2-user-facing-v1.md` only
- Therapist Layer 2: `specs/chat-03/chat-03-layer2-content-library-v2.md` only
